File transfer tool.
Author: cuz
----------------------
[commands]            [explanations]
push                  publish a file and wait for pulling from client.
pull                  pull a published file.
----------------------
[example]
On node where you want to send a file:
    >eft push file1.txt
    Pull code: XXXXXX
Then, on node where you want to receive this file:
    >eft pull XXXXXX
file1.txt will be saved to current dir on pull node.